flowchart TD
    Unmatched[Unmatched transaction description]
    AI[AI classifier evaluates description]
    Decision{Confidence and proposal quality acceptable?}
    Pending[Create pending RefinementProposal]
    Review[Operator reviews proposal\nvia UI or API]
    Approve{Approve or reject?}
    Edit[Optional edit to pattern or category]
    Rule[Create enabled ClassificationRule\nsource=ai]
    JsonSync[Sync rule to classification_rules.json]
    Reject[Mark proposal rejected]
    Reprocess[Reprocess statement or wait for next matching job]

    Unmatched --> AI --> Decision
    Decision --> Pending
    Pending --> Review --> Approve
    Approve -->|Approve| Edit --> Rule --> JsonSync --> Reprocess
    Approve -->|Reject| Reject